resource.string: Query or modify the value of SPN.

Usage:
{}$ {} [set=spn]
Example: - spn SPN: MING, 16 bytes (01 4D 49 4E 47 FF FF FF FF FF FF FF FF FF FF FF FF)
- spn set=SIMCARD SPN: MING, 16 bytes (01 4D 49 4E 47 FF FF FF FF FF FF FF FF FF FF FF FF) >>>> SIMCARD, 16 bytes (01 53 49 4D 43 41 52 44 FF FF FF FF FF FF FF FF FF)
